Full-cycle coordination for US-based international development 
foundation events running simultaneous formats across a single 
production: conferences, gala dinners, guided tours, keynote 
presentations, roundtable meetings, workshops, recreational 
activities, and exhibitions — across both editions.
End-to-end logistics and on-site coordination for this 
high-profile regional forum bringing together international 
donors and development organisations across Central America.

