supported by UNESCO/KIX.

**AHIBA Cybersecurity Events — Multiple editions**  
Coordinated multiple editions of this institutional 
cybersecurity forum including sponsorship prospecting, 
exhibitor logistics, accommodation management, and 
on-site operations.

